      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey so im about 5 months pregnant and i have this really bad sinus infection that just wont go away. my head feels like it's gonna explode lol. i have some pseudoephedrine left over from before i was pregnant, is it okay if i take a couple to help with the congestion so i can actually sleep??",
